a json array used to replace colors within the application. Example:
```json
[
  {
    "name": "sceneAtlas",
    "valueString": "100,100,100,255"
  },
  {
    "name": "bg",
    "valueString": "100,100,100,255"
  }
]
```

a json array used to replace strings within the application. Example:
```json
[
  {
    "name": "coins",
    "valueString": "Gems"
  },
  {
    "name": "lives",
    "valueString": "lives"
  }
]
```

a json object used by the scene atlas to position sprites. Example:
```json
{
  "pShootingOffset": [
    {
      "name": "x",
      "valueString": "2.2"
    },
    {
      "name": "y",
      "valueString": "-0.3"
    }
  ],
  "e1ShootingOffset": [
    {
      "name": "x",
      "valueString": "0.25"
    },
    {
      "name": "y",
      "valueString": "0.5"
    }
  ]
}
```

